      "order": 1,
      "instruction": "Heat olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat."
    },
    {
      "order": 2,
      "instruction": "Sauté garlic, carrot and onion until softened - around 5 minutes."
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "instruction": "Cook off tomato paste: Add tomato paste, bay leaf and thyme. Cook 2 minutes."
    },
    {
      "order": 4,
      "instruction": "Add lentils, simmer 15 minutes: Add lentils, stock, salt and pepper. Stir, bring to simmer, then lower heat and simmer without a lid for 15 minutes until the lentils are soft (don&#39;t let them overcook so they become mushy!)."
